---

This repository contains the open security engine:
  - AI-native security scanners (tools/01-13)
  - Shared scanner library and background-agent SDK (tools/lib, tools/sdk)
  - Python and JavaScript client SDKs (packages/zenux-sdk, packages/zenux-sdk-js)
  - Claude Code credential-leak detection hook (tools/zenux_claude_hook.sh)
  - The OpenAPI finding-ingestion contract (openapi.yaml)

The hosted multi-tenant control plane, billing, organization IAM, and
deployment automation are NOT part of this repository.
